            <div type="apparatus">
               <p>PENDING</p>
            </div>
            <div type="translation">
                <p>The birth of the Virgin, salvation. Rejoice, O world, seeing your resurrection.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>A cross with rays in the angles marks the beginning of the text. The words σωτηρία, χάρηθι, κόσμε, ανάστασιν are misspelled. Accents and breathings with errors.</p>
            </div>
